<p>The 43-year-old Colombian singer looked absolutely stunning on Monday, as she posted a racy snap to her 68 million Instagram followers.</p>

<p>'This is a new bathing suit I designed and my friend Bego made for me,' the Hips Don't Lie singer captioned the post, adding: 'I always need to create my own for the summer!' </p>

